import firebase from "firebase"
import 'firebase/storage'

var firebaseConfig = {
  apiKey: "",
  authDomain: "",
  databaseURL: "",
  projectId: "",
  storageBucket: "",
  messagingSenderId: "",
  appId: "",
  measurementId: ""
};



firebase.initializeApp(firebaseConfig);

export default firebase
